result.title: App crashes when opening the settings menu
result.steps: 1.Open the app. 2.Tap on the settings icon. 3.App crashes immediately.
result.expected: Settings menu should open without crashing.
result.actual: App crashes immediately when settings menu is opened.

result.title: Text input field does not accept characters
result.steps:
1. Go to the login page.
2. Try to type in the username field.
(3) Characters do not appear.
result.expected: Text input field does not accept characters
result.actual: Characters do not appear when typing in the input field.

result.title: Navigation bar disappears after scrolling
result.steps:
1. Open the app.
2. Scroll down on the homepage.
3. The navigation bar disappears.

result.title: Images fail to load in gallery view
result.steps: 1. Go to the gallery page. 2. Try to load images. 3. Images fail to load or display as broken links.

result.title: Error message appears on checkout page.
result.steps: 1. Add items to cart. 2. Proceed to checkout. 3. An error message appears during payment.

result.title: Dropdown menu not responsive on mobile devices
result.steps: 1. Open the website on mobile. 2. Try to click on the dropdown menu. 3. The dropdown menu does not respond.

result.title: User profile picture upload fails
result.steps:
1. Go to the user profile page.
2. Click 'Upload Picture'.
3. Upload a profile picture.
4. The image fails to upload.

result.title: Slow loading time on search results page
result.steps: 1. Go to the search page. 2. Enter a search term. 3. The search results page takes several seconds to load.
result.expected: Search results should load quickly.
result.actual: Search results take a long time to load, causing delays.

result.title: Text formatting issue in the blog editor
result.steps:
1. Open the blog editor.
2. Try to change the text color.
3. Text does not change color properly.
result.expected: The text color should change according to selection.
result.actual: The text does not change color when selected.

result.title: Page layout breaks on smaller screens
result.steps: 1. Open the website on a mobile device. 2. Navigate to the homepage. 3. The page layout breaks and becomes unreadable.
result.expected: The page layout should be responsive and readable on all screen sizes.
result.actual: The page layout breaks on smaller screens, making content difficult to read.

result.title: Submit button does not work on the contact form
result.steps:
1. Open the contact form.
2. Fill in all fields.
3. Click the submit button.
4. Nothing happens.
result.expected: The form should submit successfully without any issues.
result.actual: The submit button does not work; nothing happens when clicked.

result.title: Audio not playing on video page
result.steps:
1. Open the video page.
2. Play any video.
3. The video plays, but there is no audio.

result.title: Image carousel not working on homepage
result.steps:
1. Go to the homepage.
2. Try to navigate the image carousel.
3. Carousel does not move or change images.

result.title: Password reset link not working
result.steps: 1. Go to the password reset page. 2. Enter email and submit request. 3. No email is received.
result.expected: Password reset email should be sent to the user.
result.actual: Password reset email is not sent.

result.title: Pop-up notification not disappearing after action
result.steps: 1. Trigger a pop-up notification. 2. Perform the action to dismiss it. 3. The notification stays on the screen.
result.expected: Pop-up notification should disappear after the action is completed.
result.actual: Pop-up notification remains on the screen after the action.

result.title: Error loading user profile page
result.steps:
1. Login to the account.
2. Go to the profile page.
3. The page fails to load, showing an error message.

result.title: Search bar not functioning after update
result.steps:
1. Open the search page.
2. Try entering a search query.
3. Search bar does not register input.

result.title: Page layout is distorted on mobile devices
result.steps: 1. Open the website on a mobile device. 2. The page layout is misaligned, causing content to be unreadable.

result.title: Video player controls missing on fullscreen mode
result.steps: (1) Open the video page. (2) Click on the fullscreen button. (3) Video controls are no longer visible in fullscreen mode.
result.expected: Video controls should remain visible when in fullscreen mode.
result.actual: Video controls are no longer visible in fullscreen mode.

result.title: Form validation error not showing
result.steps: 1. Open the contact form. 2. Leave a required field blank and submit. 3. No validation error appears.
result.expected: The form should show a validation error if a required field is left blank. However, the actual behavior observed is that no validation error appears, and the form is submitted incorrectly.

result.title: Pop-up modal freezes after clicking close button
result.steps:
1. Open the website.
2. Click on any pop-up modal.
3. Click the close button.
4. The modal freezes and does not close.

result.title: User login fails after password change
result.steps:
1. Change your password.
2. Try to log in with the new password.
3. Login fails.

result.title: Broken link in footer section
result.steps: 1. Scroll down to the footer section. 2. Click on any of the links in the footer. 3. The link redirects to a 404 error page.

result.title: Text alignment issue in product description
result.steps:
1. Go to the product page.
2. Look at the product description.
3. Text is misaligned.
result.expected: The text should be aligned properly in the product description.
result.actual: The text is misaligned and looks uneven.
